UID:10000422-1778086800-1778095800@bluewaterbaltimore.org
SUMMARY:State of the Watershed
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a first look at our most recent year of water quality data\, and hear directly from your Baltimore Harbor Waterkeeper and our partners about what we’re doing (and what YOU can do) to help improve our water. \n\n\n\nTickets and more information coming soon!
URL:https://bluewaterbaltimore.org/event/state-of-the-watershed/
LOCATION:IMET\, 701 East Pratt Street\, Baltimore\, Maryland\, 21202
END:VEVENT
